## API Endpoints Reference

### Core
- `GET /api/status` — Health + Kite connection + simulation mode
- `GET/POST /api/permission` — READONLY / EXECUTE toggle

### Holdings & Portfolio
- `GET /api/holdings` — All holdings with live prices + summary
- `POST /api/import/csv/detect` — Auto-detect CSV columns
- `POST /api/import/csv` — Import CSV with column mapping
- `POST /api/import/json` — Import JSON holdings
- `POST /api/import/manual` — Add single holding
- `POST /api/import/kite` — Fetch from Kite API
- `DELETE /api/holdings/:symbol` — Delete holding
- `GET/POST /api/portfolios` — List/save portfolio snapshots
- `POST /api/portfolios/:id/load` — Load snapshot
- `DELETE /api/portfolios/:id` — Delete snapshot
- `GET /api/collateral` — Collateral + margin summary

### Scanner & Execution
- `POST /api/scan` — Run strategy + arbitrage scanner
- `GET/POST /api/recommendations` — Filter scan results
- `GET /api/arbitrage` — Arbitrage opportunities
- `POST /api/execute` — Place order (requires EXECUTE mode)

### Positions & Trades
- `GET /api/positions` — Active positions
- `POST /api/positions/:id/close` — Close position
- `POST /api/positions/:id/roll` — Roll to next expiry
- `GET /api/positions/:id/adjustments` — Adjustment suggestions
- `POST /api/positions/:id/adjust` — Execute adjustment
- `GET /api/trades` — Trade history (filterable)
- `GET /api/trades/:id` — Single trade detail

### Analytics
- `GET /api/analytics/summary` — P&L stats
- `GET /api/analytics/strategy` — By strategy breakdown
- `GET /api/analytics/monthly` — Monthly P&L (12 months)
- `GET /api/analytics/daily` — Daily P&L by date range

### Settings & Config
- `GET/POST /api/settings` — All settings CRUD
- `GET/POST /api/settings/risk-profile` — Risk profile
- `POST /api/settings/circuit-breaker` — Circuit breaker toggle
- `GET /api/safety/caps` — Hard safety limits (read-only)

### Notifications
- `GET /api/notifications` — Paginated notifications
- `GET /api/notifications/unread-count` — Unread count
- `POST /api/notifications/:id/read` — Mark read
- `POST /api/notifications/read-all` — Mark all read
- `DELETE /api/notifications/:id` — Delete

### Risk & Fees
- `GET /api/risk/status` — Risk metrics
- `GET /api/risk/alerts` — Risk alerts
- `GET /api/fees/estimate` — Fee calculation
- `GET /api/fees/summary` — Fee history

### Auth & Kite
- `GET /api/kite/login` — Login URL + auth status
- `GET /api/callback` — OAuth callback
- `POST /api/kite/auto-login` — Trigger TOTP auto-login

### Audit & GTT
- `GET /api/audit/orders` — Order audit log
- `GET /api/gtt/active` — Active GTT orders
- `DELETE /api/gtt/:id` — Cancel GTT

### Daily Summary
- `GET /api/daily-summary` — Today's summary
- `GET /api/daily-summary/:date` — Summary by date

---

## Database Schema (10 tables in models.py)

| Table | PK | Purpose |
|-------|-----|---------|
| `trades` | `id` UUID | Trade entries/exits, P&L, strategy, fees |
| `positions` | `id` UUID | Active options, Greeks, margin, expiry |
| `holdings` | `symbol` TEXT | Stock holdings (qty, avg_price, ltp) |
| `portfolio_snapshots` | `id` UUID | Saved portfolio snapshots |
| `notifications` | `id` UUID | System notifications |
| `daily_summary` | `date` TEXT | Daily aggregates |
| `settings` | `key` TEXT | Key-value config store |
| `order_audit` | `id` UUID | Order placement history |
| `gtt_orders` | `id` UUID | GTT stop-loss orders |
| `adjustments` | `id` UUID | Position adjustment history |

