## Environment Variables

### Backend (set in Azure Container App or .env)
```
KITE_API_KEY, KITE_API_SECRET, KITE_USER_ID      # Zerodha broker
KITE_TOTP_SECRET                                    # Auto-login TOTP seed
SQLITE_DB_PATH          # Default: data/yield_engine.db
PORT                     # Default: 8000
FLASK_SECRET_KEY         # For TOTP encryption
ENVIRONMENT              # Default: Development
MAX_LOTS_NIFTY=2, MAX_LOTS_BANKNIFTY=1, MAX_LOTS_STOCK=2  # Safety caps
MAX_ORDER_VALUE=500000, MAX_ORDERS_PER_DAY=20
```

### Frontend (build-time)
```
VITE_API_BASE            # API base URL (empty = relative URLs)
```

